{
 "file": "_STGSP2A.bin",
 "source_size": 37628,
 "built_size": 40437,
 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1556",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看到了！是新吉翁的舰队！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6e7d7e7ba06e7b6ef8ae7d9ee88e7b4e7d4e7c9060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1584",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不是说好、要按约定的方式进入的吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7b6e7ede7c702ef2aea76e9ace867e7b4efb1ea26e892e891e7b4e80205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15b6",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "数量倒是对得上……",
   "zh_hex": "15e914e851e848e7b6e7bee80ab2090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15c7",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、不对！似乎比情报上多出了一艘！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e7b5e7be06e944e933e825e88be913b2e7e9afe7ba87eb1806000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15f9",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚这人、很坦率啊",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d6e7b9efb202e981e843e9e1e7c3000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1605",
   "jp_len": 41,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他很清楚、联邦只要拿出真本事、灭新吉{00}翁一百回都轻而易举",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce981e995ebd302ef2ed1ef32ef2ae9a7afe820d2a902e8e1ef8ae7d900ee8887ebdc8ce840e990e89ce964ea2100000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x162e",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正因如此、他才这样寻求谈判、这是个明{00}智的判断",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3bef33e7f0e7ca02e80ce836e7b9e7daefe2e93aeaf4eb2902e7b9e7b6e828ef3900ec74e7b4eb29e9820000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1665",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1691",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "联邦那帮家伙、看来是彻底松懈下来了啊{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2eefaae7b7e910e7dfe7fd02e7f6efcfe7b6ebc5e9b4e9e0ec6fef4defcfe7bae7c300090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16ac",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好！抛掉假目标！立刻转入攻击！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7ef97eaa9e9d3eb28efd4e96fef97e86be91fe9c2e891ef67e7ccef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x16ec",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "参、参谋次官阁下！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ed1a02ed1aea6ee8648fe8d789060600000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1716",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟然是MS！？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ce7efe7b6efa7ef9eef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1744",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎、怎么可能……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f202e7f2e7bde7c4e7c60909ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1750",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这样一来、可就违反条约了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7daefb6efcf02e7c4e7c5eab2e87ce9d4e9ace7ba0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1783",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌方战力、已被全歼！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3d0ef28da02ef3ae7f1bbeaaf06060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17b6",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "好！MS部队就这样朝月神2……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c7061314cce7c9e7c5e7b9e7daeaade850e9aa0f09090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17fc",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么、竟是隆德·贝尔！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bd02ef2ce7b6ed16e82cef4be857e7e1ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1831",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "果然、那投降是假的！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e871e7ef02e7b7e948e943e7b6eb28e7b4ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1842",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "全舰、第1种战斗配置！迎击新吉翁舰队{00}！！",
   "zh_hex": "15bbe7d402e9400ee7d1ef28e7ffea34ea0e06e931e7ccef8ae7d9ee88e7d4e7c9000606000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1882",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我可不会让你得逞！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7c4e7b5e7e2e7f9e7b8e80ae9ebef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18c1",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是邱尼·加斯！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6efa2e896ef4be854e7c8ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18f0",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要干掉他们、这场作战就等于赢定了！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2ae8d3e9d3e80ce7bb02e7b9e876ef2fef28e7c5e826e879e9cbe867e7baef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x190d",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "岂能眼睁睁放过这大好的胜机！！",
   "zh_hex": "15eac3e7c6e90bed90ed90e86cef36e7b9efa5e7c7e7b4e8dbe7e4ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x194e",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啧！强化人这种东西、就是这样……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9faef97e8ade9a5efb2e7b9e7d1e8bae7f802e7c5e7b6e7b9e7da0909ef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1962",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我去给邱尼队打掩护！",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce7ebe839efa2e896e7c9e7f5ec72e8e0ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1999",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌方MS、好像正朝我们冲过来了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3efb1efa7ef9e02e7c7e8e9ef3beaadefcce7bbe95eef36efcfe7baef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19c6",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "既然送上门来、那正合我意！就此投入战{00}斗！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8c4e7efe9baef4ce90cefcf02e7b7ef3befc0efccef3cef97e7c5e7cae948e891ef2800e7ffef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19e0",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "全舰、开始战斗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb4e7d402e7fae908ef28e7ffef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a4c",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "战斗、已经打响了……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef28e7ff02ef3ae8b7e7f5ecbfe7ba0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a58",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿姆罗他、果然也在战斗吗……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e823e7ece80c02e871e7efe7c0ef29ef28e7ffe802090905000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a93",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "待在那儿的、是什么人！？",
   "zh_hex": "15eaa8ef29e7b7eb7ce7b402e7b6e7dde7bdefb2ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1aef",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！？你、你……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def9705e7b802e7b80909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b19",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "被发现了吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f1e870e82fe7bae802ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b3c",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！？你说是奎丝·帕拉雅！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bdef9705e7b8e7ede7b6eb82e8a3ef4beb01e7c2ebfdef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b69",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看样子、她是躲进了货舱区里",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6e7dae88602e88ee7b6ea6fe892e7baeaf5ebebef35ef31000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b7d",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "毕竟、那孩子好像对阿姆罗大尉有意思…{00}…",
   "zh_hex": "15ea2cef2c02e7b7e956e886e7c7e8e9e7bee7d2e823e7ecefa5efc6e7cbef3cefca090009000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bb3",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "现在哪还顾得上那些！眼下可是战斗当中{00}啊！",
   "zh_hex": "15e82fef29e8ffe7f7ea1fe80aef4ce7b7e8a4ef97e90bef4de7c4e7b6ef28e7ffef53ef4e00e7c3ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1be9",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是、是！那位小姐她……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b602e7b6ef97e7b7e834e83ee921e88e0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c1b",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "战斗结束之前、我也分不出手、先随便找{00}个房间把她安置好！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef28e7ffe868e895e7cdef5102efcce7c0efaee7b5efbeef6602ef8be9a1e8fae9d200e828ecd8e8fce81be88ee7fcea0ee7c7ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c57",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……明、明白了！",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef3902ef39e809e7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c7e",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真是的……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e820e7b6e7b40909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c9e",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "成功了吗……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e837e9b1e7bae8020909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cc4",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不……夏亚不在里面",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b50909ef37e7d6e7b5ef29ef31e8620000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cec",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "而且新吉翁军的数量、也比上次交战时要{00}少……",
   "zh_hex": "15e89ce999ef8ae7d9ee88e7e0e7b4e914e85102e7c0e825b2e864e861ef28ef2def2a00b1090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d25",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "莫非、是有什么隐情吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15eba0e8f002e7b6e7cbe7dde7bdeb73e88be802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d58",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我怎么会、任凭你们这帮家伙为所欲为！{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7f2e7bde7e202e89aea49e7b8e7bbe7b9e910e7dfe7fde7c1e7fbeacbe7c1ef9700ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d97",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那家伙……是刚才那个！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7dfe7fd0909e7b6e8bce836e7b7e828ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1dc8",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "事到如今、哪怕只击沉隆德·贝尔的旗舰{00}也好……！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb8e7d7e7f0efb902e8ffe958ef32e7cce983ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7b4eb0be7d400e7c0e7c70909ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e06",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……休想得逞！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e90ee7e6e80ae9ebef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e42",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "他可是我重要的部下……",
   "zh_hex": "15e80ce7c4e7b6efcce8a1ef2ae7b4ef70ef4d0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e76",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这种地方、我可不能让你得手！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7d1ef63efb102efcce7c4e7b5e7c6e7f9e7b8e80aef66ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ea4",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚……！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d60909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ec7",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "大佐他……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15efa5efbae80c0909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1eeb",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "作战成功了、邱尼、阿克西斯已经落入我{00}们手中",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2fef28e837e9b1e7ba02efa2e89602e7d2e7d5e7f8e7c8ef3ae8b7e92ae891efcc00e7bbef66ef4e00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f06",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "无需再战……撤！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dce92de80bef280909e90aef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f62",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚……别想逃！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d60909e7e5e7e6e8c2ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f94",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚！曾与我们并肩作战的你、为何要毁{00}灭地球！？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d6ef97ea2ae832efcce7bbe957eb16ef2fef28e7b4e7b802e7c1efbcef2ae97c00e8e1ef63efd3ef9705000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fe9",
   "jp_len": 41,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "留在地球上的那些人、只会污染地球、是{00}被重力束缚了灵魂的人们！",
   "zh_hex": "15e98cef29ef63efd3ef4ce7b4e7b7e8a4efb202ef32e7e2ec26ebd0ef63efd302e7b600e7f1e8a1efb0e895eb9be7baeaebeb4ae7b4efb2e7bbef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2041",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "地球、根本容不下人类所有的私欲！",
   "zh_hex": "15bf9502e9b8d2ed2fe7b589b4e841e7fbe7cbe7b4a8eacb060000000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2066",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你要明白这一点啊、阿姆罗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8ef2aef39e809e7b9efb6e822e7c302e7d2e823e7ecef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20a6",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……你在说什么！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909e7b8ef29e7ede7dde7bdef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20ba",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "人类的智慧、足以跨越那种东西！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb2e841e7b4ec74ee2402ea1ee7f3eeacea57e7b7e7d1e8bae7f8ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20ff",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那你就立刻、把智慧赐予那群愚民、给我{00}看看！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b8e7c5e86be91f02e81bec74ee24eff2efb7e7b7ecfae959ef3802e839efcc00e7f6e7f6ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2148",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "少来这一套！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efacefcfe7b9efb6eb30ef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2181",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "到此为止了……夏亚！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d7e7cae7c1e869e7ba0909ef37e7d6ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21bd",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21f6",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21fe",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "总得有人来背负起人类的罪业、向地球赎{00}罪才行！",
   "zh_hex": "15e881e80ae7cbefb2efcfe9e4e92ce847efb2e841e7b4ea7feada02efc1ef63efd3eff100ea7fe836efd6ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2225",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你为何就不懂！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7c1efbce7c5e7b5e8b0ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2252",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你只不过、是想借这种方式、把自己的野{00}心正当化罢了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8ef32e7b5ef3602e7b6e7e6eadce7b9e7d1efb1ea2602e81befb5e8c9e7b4eb2100e82def3bef53e9a5eaefe7baef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x228f",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿尔黛西亚……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e7e1ea9ae7f8e7d60909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22bd",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "该结束了、夏亚……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e898e868e895e7ba02ef37e7d60909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22f0",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d0909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x231d",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……这是怎么回事！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b9e7b6e7f2e7bdef52efb8ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x234c",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们这帮人、一拥而上……喂、这也太赖{00}皮了吧！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbe7b9e910efb202efb6eb35e89cef4c0909e8bd02e7b9e7c0e86aeb4600ebdde7bae7d0ef970500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2386",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "奎丝！？",
   "zh_hex": "15eb82e8a3ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23b2",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "奎丝！！",
   "zh_hex": "15eb82e8a3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23b9",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你到底、明不明白自己在做什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7d7e9b402ef39e7b5ef39e809efb5e8c9ef29e81ce7dde7bdef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23ed",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我知道啦！！",
   "zh_hex": "158be85ae82aec0f06060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23f9",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚是真心在为地球担忧、这点你都不懂{00}吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d6e7b6e820e82def29e7c1ef63efd3e9fdee1d02e7b9e822e7b8e840e7b5e8b000e802ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2432",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "奎丝！！",
   "zh_hex": "15eb82e8a3ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2454",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿姆罗！都怪你这副样子……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e823e7ec06e840ea07e7b8e7b9ecb6e7dae8860909060000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x248a",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你是……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b60909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24ad",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我叫奎丝",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce8c1eb82e8a30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24b4",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "奎丝·艾雅哟",
   "zh_hex": "15eb82e8a3ef4be8d6ebfdeb2c0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24bd",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚大佐、你就交给我来保护吧！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d6efa5efba02e7b8e7c5e861e839efccefcfea47e8e0e7d0ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24f1",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、要跟我一起来吗？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02ef2ae973efccefb6e847efcfe8020500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x251a",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "拉·凯拉姆号上、有个讨厌的女人……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c2ef4be95fe7c2e823e833ef4c02e7cbe828e9f7eb2be7b4efadefb2090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2532",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……所以、我才在那里待不下去",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7fbe7f302efcce836ef29e7b7ef31eaa8e7b5ef4de7eb0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2567",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……奎丝！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909eb82e8a3ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x258b",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……这场闹剧、就到此为止了、阿姆罗",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b9e876ead8ecb502e7c5e7d7e7cae7c1e869e7ba02e7d2e823e7ec0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25b8",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚……你这家伙！？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d60909e7b8e7b9e7dfe7fdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25de",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你若有心和我做个了断、就到阿克西斯来{00}吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7e7e7cbe82de7d3efcce81ce828e7bae98202e7c5e7d7e7d2e7d5e7f8e7c8efcf00e7d00000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25f9",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我当真要毁灭地球……",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef53e820ef2ae97ce8e1ef63efd309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x260c",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你们若是不肯承认我、那就来阻止我给我{00}看看吧！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7bbe7e7e7b6e7b5e93dea75e8a0efcc02e7b7e7c5efcfe8efe869efcce839efcc00e7f6e7f6e7d0ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2653",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d60909ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2681",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……着了夏亚的道了",
   "zh_hex": "150909e86de7baef37e7d6e7b4e82ae7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x268f",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "刚才确认过、月神2的核弹储藏库、已经{00}被搬得一干二净了",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bce836e88ce8a0ef3602e850e9aa0fe7b4e8f3e946eddbed03e9b302ef3ae8b700e7f1ecdde80a87e8d3ea13ecb0e7ba0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26cb",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这么说、是被夏亚带走了吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7bde7ed02e7b6e7f1ef37e7d6e937e890e7bae8020909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26df",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "新吉翁、是打算让阿克西斯连同核弹一起{00}、朝地球坠落吗",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ae7d9ee8802e7b6e7f5e889e7f9e7d2e7d5e7f8e7c8e86ee85de8f3e94687e8470002eaadbf95eb53e92ae80200000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2717",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "让阿克西斯坠向地球、是吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f9e7d2e7d5e7f8e7c8eb53efc1ef63efd302e7b6e8020909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2742",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿克西斯的核脉冲引擎、目前都还能运作",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e7d5e7f8e7c8e7b4e8f3ebe9e95ee9d0ec1e02efd4ef51e840e7f7e7c6e986ef2f0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2757",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚若想确实引发核冬天、就一定会动用{00}阿克西斯本身",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d6e7e7e7e6e88ce87fe9d0e870e8f3ede4e84402e7c5efb6e867e7e2ef30efb300e7d2e7d5e7f8e7c8efa6e88d000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2796",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但联邦的其他部队呢？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbef2eefaae7b4e8cfe80cef70e7c9e907050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27a6",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "闹出这么大的动静、联邦军总该出动了吧{00}？",
   "zh_hex": "15ead8efbee7b9e7bdefa5e7b4ef30eab302ef2eefaae7e0e881e898efbeef30e7bae7d0000500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27dd",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "如今的状况是、殖民地驻留舰队怕引发暴{00}动、根本动弹不得",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f0efb9e7b4e98be8d0e7b602e8a9ef38ef63eca2e98ce7d4e7c9e958e9d0e870ea4f00ef3002e9b8efa6ef30e946e7b5e80a0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2814",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这岂不就像、殖民地在替夏亚撑腰一样吗{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9eac3e7b5e7c5e8e902e8a9ef38ef63ef29ea50ef37e7d6ea29ee8fefb6e7dae80200ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x284e",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我们迪安娜回归军、恐怕也是想动却{00}动不了啊",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce7bbea11e7fce7eaef52e947e7e002eb33e958e7c0e7b6e7e6ef30eadf00ef30e7b5e7bae7c300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2864",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "擅自调动部队、只会让迪安娜大人的处境{00}更加为难",
   "zh_hex": "15eb5defb5e95cef30ef70e7c902ef32e7e2e7f9ea11e7fce7eaefa5efb2e7b4e903eb8100e952e854e7c1e8660000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28a0",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这么一来、眼下能行动的、{00}就只剩我们了吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7bd87d902e90b89e7c69fef30e7b40200e7c5ef32ea3a8be7bbe7bae8020909000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28d6",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "援军指望不上、就算有、也来不及和我们{00}会合了",
   "zh_hex": "15e863e7e0e8c0e965e7b5ef4c02e7c5e889e7cb02e7c0efcfe7b5e9cfe7d3efcce7bb00e7e2efc0e7ba0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x291d",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "况且、也不能把联邦政府的失败、硬推到{00}迪安娜女王头上……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d0e99902e7c0e7b5e7c6e81bef2ed1ea68ea60e7b4e8a5e88f02eb97eaabe7d700ea11e7fce7eab0e884e92eb209090000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x293f",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来、只能用现有的战力、来制定一套阻{00}止夏亚的作战了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcf02ef32e7c6efb3e82fe7cbe7b4ef28efb002efcfe8dee867efb6eb30e8ef00e869ef37e7d6e7b4ef2fef28e7ba000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2980",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这么说、能用的手段、{00}就只剩舰队攻击了吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7bde7ed02e7c6d8e7b4aeea6b0200e7c5ef32ea3ae7d4e7c99ee7cce7bae802050000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29b8",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "从外部破坏行不通的话、也还有从内部炸{00}毁这一招",
   "zh_hex": "15e88ae8f7ccc7e9ed9fe7b5c2e7b4e81f02e7c0e7f7e7cbe88ae99acce9c900e97ce7b987e97a0000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29fa",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、首要目标就是破坏核脉冲引擎……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02ef40ef2aefd4e96fe7c5e7b6ef6de9ede8f3ebe9e95ee9d0ec1e0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a13",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "若是行不通、就再从内部进行破坏、是这{00}个作战吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e7e7b6efd6e7b5ef5902e7c5e80be88ae99aef70e892efd6ef6de9ed02e7b6e7b900e828ef2fef28e7d0000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a52",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来、也只有这个办法了……好！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcf02e7c0ef32e7cbe7b9e828e8eae84ee7ba0909e7c7ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a66",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、就趁敌人备战完毕之前、把这事做{00}个了断！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7c5e9eae7e3efb2e877ef28e87eea2ce7cdef5102e81be7b9efb8e81c00e828e7bae982ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a96",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ac0",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……舰长！前进航线上发现1艘舰船！是{00}扎夫特！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7d4ef34ef97ef51e892e9c1e916ef4ce870e82feff7eb18e7d4ea02ef97e7b600e84be830e7cfef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2af3",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你说是扎夫特！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7ede7b6e84be830e7cfef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b13",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "百忙之中打扰、实在抱歉",
   "zh_hex": "15ebdcea06e7cdef4ee7f5ebc702e87fef29e922e9270000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b21",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是PLANT议长吉尔伯特·迪兰达尔",
   "zh_hex": "158be7b6eed4e81aea9ceed3eed6e8e3ef34e7d9e7e1eaa4e7cf04ea11e86fef2be7e100000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b55",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是布莱特·诺亚大佐",
   "zh_hex": "158be7b6e831e846e7cf04e972e7d6bea300000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b61",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、您找我们、究竟有何贵干……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e835e9d2efcce7bb02e906ef2ce7cbefbce930e8d30909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b97",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "听说各位、是要去{00}阻止夏亚那个新吉翁……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8d1e7ede819e83402e7b6ef2ae7eb00e8efe869ef37e7d6e7b7e828ef8ae7d9ee88090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2bb2",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为此、我们PLANT、也想向各位提供援助",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7ca028be7bbeed4e81aea9ceed3eed602e7c0e7e69de819e834e821eca9e863ea2300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2bed",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那真是……求之不得的好意、{00}可究竟是为何……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e820e7b60909e93ae7cde7b5e80ae7b4e7c7ef3c0200e7c4e906ef2ce7b6e7c18a0909050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c1d",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贵舰上、同行着几位对我们PLANT{00}而言极为重要的人物",
   "zh_hex": "15e930e7d4b202e85d9fe86deaa5e834e7be8be7bbeed4e81aea9ceed3eed600e89c9beacae7c1e8a1ef2ae7b4b4e99e00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c39",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "贵队的安危、对我们而言、同样是不可忽{00}视的大事",
   "zh_hex": "15e930e7c9e7b4e7fce93502e7be8be7bbe89c9b02e85de7dae7b6e7b5e7c4ed7700e9d9e7b4bea9000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c72",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您指的是、拉克丝……吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e835e8c0e7b4e7b602e7c2e7d5e8a30909e80205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ca2",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还有你",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7e7cbe7b80000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2cab",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不、要说隆德·贝尔本身就是一群重要人{00}物的集合、也毫不为过",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b502ef2ae7eded16e82c04e857e7e1d2e88de7c5e7b687ecfae8a1ef2ab400e99ee7b4ea98a002e7c0ea0ae7b5e7c1ef36000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ccd",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哪怕动用扎夫特也要守护的存在、说的正{00}是你们",
   "zh_hex": "15e8ffe958ef30efb3e84be830e7cfe7c0ef2ae8a8e8e0e7b4e993ef2902e7ede7b4ef3b00e7b6e7b8e7bb000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d37",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、碍于和联邦的条约、我们也无法公{00}然出动军队",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e8c6e879e7d3ef2eefaae7b4e9d4e9ac02efcce7bbe7c0e7dce84ee9a400e7efefbeef30e7e0e7c90000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d59",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "作为替代、我们希望、能为各位提供可充{00}当战力的MS",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2fe7c1ea50e8e702efcce7bbe87be96502e7c6e7c1e819e834e821eca9e7c4ea8600ef53ef28efb0e7b4efa7ef9e00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d93",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是MS……吗",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6efa7ef9e0909e802000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2db8",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "ZGMF-X23S、救世主高达、这是{00}我们扎夫特的最新型MS",
   "zh_hex": "15eedaeed113eca5ef71eed90f101402e8cae83ce954e812ef2b02e7b9e7b6008be7bbe84be830e7cfe7b4e8c5ef8ae9771314000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e0f",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿姆罗……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e823e7ec09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e31",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "倩恩、你怎么了、一脸这么担心的样子？",
   "zh_hex": "15ed4ae7ee02e7b8e7f2e7bde7ba0287eb69e7b9e7bde9fde82de7b4e7dae886050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e61",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我担心的、是你呀、阿姆罗",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce9fde82de7b402e7b6e7b8e9c602e7d2e823e7ec00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e8a",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不会有事的、{00}ν高达不也是你亲手调整的吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5e7e2e7cba9e7b40200e8fee812ef2be7b5e7c0e7b6e7b8e894aee95ce9fee7b4e802050000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ec3",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯……",
   "zh_hex": "15e86509090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2eca",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只是、那精神感应框架它……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32e7b602e7b7e98de9aae87de873eef3e99de97809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ef2",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "精神感应框架？",
   "zh_hex": "15e98de9aae87de873eef3e99d050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f15",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "它会和大尉的感应装置产生共振、据说会{00}引出未知的机能……",
   "zh_hex": "15e978e7e2e7d3efa5efc6e7b4e87de873e98fea0eec05ef8dea48eb5b02e8cce7ede7e200e9d0efbee8b4e85ae7b4e7e4e7c609090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f52",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你是指奥克特伯说的那事吗？{00}那是没影的事",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b6e8c0e82be7d5e7cfeaa4e7ede7b4e7b7a9e8020500e7b7e7b6e7d8ea8ee7b4a9000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2fd7",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "诶？是精神感应框架吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15eaf305e7b6e98de9aae87de873eef3e99de80205000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ffe",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "总觉得、那似乎并不是阿纳海姆造出来的{00}技术",
   "zh_hex": "15e881e8aee80a02e7b7e944e933e957e7b5e7b6e7d2e882e91be823e93eefbeefcfe7b400ea64ebce00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3034",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可是、那又是从哪儿……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7b602e7b7e8f1e7b6e88ae8ffeb7c09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x305a",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说还无法断定、但恐怕……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7ede7f7e7dce84ee982e86702e7dbeb33e9580909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x30f1",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "倩恩、你什么都不用担心",
   "zh_hex": "15ed4ae7ee02e7b8e7dde7bde840e7b5d8e9fde82d000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x311e",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "阿姆罗……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d2e823e7ec09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3140",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "ν高达由我来做基础设计、再交给你来维{00}护整备……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8fee812ef2be8a6efccefcfe81ce829eb96eb43ea5502e80be861e839e7b8efcfea5400e8e0e9fee87709090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3161",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我们一定能赢",
   "zh_hex": "150909efcce7bbefb6e867e7c6e9cb000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3188",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯……说得也是呢、阿姆罗",
   "zh_hex": "15e8650909e7ede80ae7c0e7b6e90702e7d2e823e7ec000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x31af",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……大佐！",
   "zh_hex": "150909efa5efbaef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x31d2",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯……是奎丝啊、怎么了？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8650909e7b6eb82e8a3e7c302e7f2e7bde7ba050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x31fb",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、难道只是拉拉的替身吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "158b02e866e82aef32e7b6e7c2e7c2e7b4ea50e88de80206050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x322b",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "奎丝……！",
   "zh_hex": "15eb82e8a30909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x324e",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我、可是真心爱着大佐您的呀！？",
   "zh_hex": "15efcc02e7c4e7b6e820e82de8d5e86defa5efbae835e7b4e9c6ef97050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3265",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3287",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这可真叫人为难……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7c4e820e8c1efb2e7c1e8660909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x32ac",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x32b3",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "只要是为了大佐、我连死都不怕！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef32ef2ae7b6e7c1e7baefa5efba02efcce86eef6ae840e7b5e958ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x32e7",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是吗",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e8020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x32ef",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那、我便忘了拉拉吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b702efcce8faea4de7bae7c2e7c2e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3319",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊哈！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c3e7e8060000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3321",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、我就驾着阿尔法、来守护大佐您！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02efcce7c5e953e86de7d2e7e1e84e02efcfe8a8e8e0efa5efbae835ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7fb2",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不好！这艘舰要是被击沉、那可就{00}……！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5e7c706e7b9eb18e7d4ef2ae7b6e7f1e7cce98302e7b7e7c4e7c500090906000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x7ffe",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那样一来、根本就救不了地球啊、{00}克瓦特罗！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7da87d902e9b8d2e7c5e8cae7b5e7babf95e7c30200e7d5e99fe7cfe7ec06060000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8046",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "挑起这种、{00}只会让悲伤不断扩散开来的战争……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15eae7e847e7b9e7d10200ef32e7e2e7f9e9dfe8f9e7b5e982ec1aa4e7fad9e7b4ef28e85209090606000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8080",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "现在的你、和西罗克、克鲁泽之流没什么{00}两样！夏亚·阿兹纳布尔！",
   "zh_hex": "15e82fef29e7b4e7b802e7d3e7f8e7ece7d502e7d5e8a2e984e7cdea2ee7d8e7dde7bd00e97de7da06ef37e7d604e7d2e856e882e831e7e1060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x80b7",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "卡缪、捷多！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e801e91702e7bce7e9ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x80ef",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8154",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我希望你、能跟我一起走、哈曼",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce87be965e7b802e7c6e973efccefb6e847e89002e7e8e874000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x81c2",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "有我在你身边、所以、{00}你尽管放心吧、哈曼",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cb8bef29e7b8e88de89902e7fbe7f30200e7b8e8f2e93be86ce82de7d002e7e8e8740000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8233",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你又一次离我而去、我还以为、自己早已{00}把对你的思念斩断了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e8f1efb6e864e901efcce89ce7eb02efcce7f7e7f3e7c102efb5e8c9e963ef3a00e81be7bee7b8e7b4efcaea27ed71e982e7ba0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8258",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可我却仍……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4efcceadfeab909090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8265",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x828f",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x82f4",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我希望你、能跟我一起走、哈曼",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce87be965e7b802e7c6e973efccefb6e847e89002e7e8e874000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8362",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "有我在你身边、所以、{00}你尽管放心吧、哈曼",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cb8bef29e7b8e88de89902e7fbe7f30200e7b8e8f2e93be86ce82de7d002e7e8e8740000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x83d3",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你又一次离我而去、我还以为、自己早已{00}把对你的思念斩断了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e8f1efb6e864e901efcce89ce7eb02efcce7f7e7f3e7c102efb5e8c9e963ef3a00e81be7bee7b8e7b4efcaea27ed71e982e7ba0909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x83f8",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可我却仍……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4efcceadfeab909090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8405",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夏亚……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef37e7d609090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8472",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一路辛苦了",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e8d2ea58e9e6e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x847f",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "感谢你将这条『宇宙世纪路线』一路游玩{00}到了最后",
   "zh_hex": "15e87de8b2e7b8e84ae7b9e9d40ce8bee8bfe83ceb99e8d2e9160defb6e8d2ea94e97000e7d7e7bae8c5e7fe000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x849f",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、隆德·贝尔队的征战、就先在此告{00}一段落了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7b4ecd2ef2802e7c5ef8bef29e7cae8e500efb6ea6be92ae7ba09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x84be",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过游戏本身仍可继续下去、今后也请你{00}继续尽情享受",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9adef4de7eb02efb9e7fee7c0e83ae7b800e9d6e9ade8f2e88bec06e8c800000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x84e3",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、为一路通关本路线的你、还专门准{00}备了一个特别关卡",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702e7c1efb6e8d2ef59e8bbefa6e8d2e916e7b4e7b802e7f7eb4be90ce87a00e877e7baefb6e828e7cfe7e5e8bbe8010000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x850a",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是和我们分头作战、一直战斗至今的大{00}天使队之间的特别演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e7d3efcce7bbefaee92eef2fef2802efb6e875ef28e7ffe897efb9e7b4efa500e844e83fe7c9e7cde8fce7b4e7cfe7e5ea2feab6000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x852b",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "和他们交手一番、亲自检验你培养至今的{00}部队实力、也是件好事",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d3e80ce7bbe861ef66efb6ee6d02e894efb5ee40ea99e7b8edfeec0be897efb9e7b400ef70e7c9e87fefb002e7c0e7b6e991e7c7efb8000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8550",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特别演习』、便能与{00}他们一决高下",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29abe8a6e7beef28c0e966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d02e8fae7c6e83200e80ce7bb87e8abe812890000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8575",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、就请继续游玩『SD高达G世{00}代DS』吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83ae9d6e9adea94e9700cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83c00e8e7ef96ef9e0de7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8599",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也希望你能静下心来、尽情玩到最后",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0e87be965e7b8e7c6eab3ef4de82defcf02e8f2e88be970e7d7e8c5e7fe00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8612",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "谢谢你一路以来、一直陪着我这个不太靠{00}得住的舰长",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b2e8b2e7b8efb6e8d2e7f3efcf02efb6e875ef42e86defcce7b9e828e7b5e86ae8c700e80ae859e7b4e7d4ef34000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8631",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『平成高达路线』、{00}就到此告一段落了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce887e837e812ef2be8d2e9160d0200e7c5e7d7e7cae8e587ea6be92ae7ba00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x864f",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说、我们预防者的这场战斗、是已经结{00}束了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7ed02efcce7bbea5ae968ef6ee7b4e7b9e876ef28e7ff02e7b6ef3ae8b7e86800e895e7ba090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8669",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……不过游戏本身也还能继续下去哦、今{00}后也请你继续享受游戏吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88de7c0e7f7e7c6e9d6e9adef4de7ebe91902efb900e7fee7c0e83ae7b8e9d6e9adec06e8c8ea94ea3ee7d000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x868f",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "为一路玩通这条路线的你、还另外准备了{00}全新的关卡哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c1efb6e8d2e970ef59e7b9e9d4e8d2e916e7b4e7b802e7f7e99be8f7e87ae877e7ba00efb4ef8ae7b4e8bbe801e91900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x86b3",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与我们分头、和提坦斯及新吉翁交过{00}手的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e8328be7bbcde92e02e7d3e821e843e7c8e9cfef8ae7d9ee88e861ef3600aee7b40909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x86ce",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……正是和那支隆德·贝尔队之间的特别{00}演习哦",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef3be7b6e7d3e7b7e883ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7cde8fce7b4e7cfe7e500ea2feab6e919000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x86e1",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特别演习』、就能和{00}他们一战了哦",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d02e7c5e7c6e7d300e80ce7bbefb6ef28e7bae9190000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8707",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请务必挑战看看哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e83ae94fe860eae7ef28e7f6e7f6e919000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8715",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、就请继续游玩『SD高达G世{00}代DS』吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83ae9d6e9adea94e9700cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83c00e8e7ef96ef9e0de7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8739",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『自由对战的战火！尽情冲杀吧、大天使{00}号！！』",
   "zh_hex": "150cefb5e8a6e7beef28e7b4ef28e8daef97e8f2e88be95ee89be7d002efa5e844e83f00e833ef97ef970d0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x87ba",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是主天使号的舰长、娜塔尔·巴基露露{00}中佐",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7b6e954e844e83fe833e7b4e7d4ef3402e7eae945e7e1ef4be85be829e858e85800ef4eefba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x87ca",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "首先、请允许我向你一路以来{00}出色的指挥、致以由衷的敬意",
   "zh_hex": "15ef40b802e83aecade8a78b9de7b887e8d2e7f3d900afe89fe7b4e8c0e94902ea32e7f3e8a6edb3e7b4ee38ef3c000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x87ec",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正是多亏了你的协助、我们才终于得以奋{00}战到最后",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3be7b6e7e9eab7e7bae7b8e7b4e8f6ea2302efcce7bbe836e8e2e879e80ae7f3ef4600ef28e7d7e8c5e7fe0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x880e",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『对手路线』、就到此结束了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce7beef66e8d2e9160d02e7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8824",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说、我们主天使队的这场战斗、是已经{00}到此结束了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7ed02efcce7bbe954e844e83fe7c9e7b4e7b9e876ef28e7ff02e7b6ef3ae8b700e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x883d",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过游戏本身仍可继续下去、今后也请你{00}继续尽情享受",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef36ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9adef4de7eb02efb9e7fee7c0e83ae7b800e9d6e9ade8f2e88bec06e8c800000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8861",
   "jp_len": 43,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "自由对战今后仍可继续下去、另外、只要{00}选择『特别演习』……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb5e8a6e7beef28efb9e7feeab9e7c4e9d6e9adef4de7eb02e99be8f702ef32ef2a00e966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x888c",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "便能与隆德·贝尔、预防者一同进行一场{00}联合演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e8fae7c6e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e102ea5ae968ef6eefb6e85de892efd6efb6e87600ef2eefc0ea2feab60000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x88aa",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我坚信、以你的本领、在与他们的战斗中{00}也定能克敌制胜",
   "zh_hex": "15efcceb80e90f02e7f3e7b8e7b4efa6ea2002ef29e832e80ce7bbe7b4ef28e7ffef4e00e7c0e867e7c6e7d5e7e3e8dee8db000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x88cf",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、就请继续游玩『SD高达G世{00}代DS』吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd02e7c5e83ae9d6e9adea94e9700cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83c00e8e7ef96ef9e0de7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x88f3",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也愿你武运长久、奋战不息",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0e961e7b8e8ece986ef34e9db02ef46ef28e7b5ec6a000000"
  }
 ]
}
